; Regression test for issue #1589: Strange balance reports (BZ#517)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1589
;
; The bug: ledger was displaying zero balances for accounts that used @@ (total
; price) cost annotations when those positions were fully closed. The zero
; balances should be elided by default. Additionally, with implicit commodity
; conversions, only one zero account was shown instead of neither.

2010/01/01 Open positions
    a   16$ @@ 10€
    b   -10€

2010/01/02 Close positions
    a   -16$
    b   10€ @@ 16$

test bal
end test

test bal -B
                -16$
                 10€  a
                 16$
                -10€  b
--------------------
                   0
end test
